Class Exit

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LastTurn, JsonSerializable

    public class Exit
extends VoiceXmlLastTurn
    Terminates a VoiceXmlDialogue with an exit, returning the control to the platform. Additional information may be returned with an expression of a list of variables.
    See Also:
    VoiceXmlDialogue, LastTurn, https://www.w3.org/TR/voicexml20/#dml5.3.9
